 *
 * V.15.0 — Major UX Redesign:
 *   - Admin/Customer split: different sections per role
 *   - Item cards with product thumbnails + lightbox
 *   - Shipping address card (admin only)
 *   - Enhanced timeline with timestamps (admin only)
